# REST API Design

## Endpoints (mẫu + submission/template)
```
GET    /api/v1/forms                 # List (with paging)
GET    /api/v1/forms/{id}            # Get one
GET    /api/v1/forms/{id}/template   # Download Excel template (.xlsx). Query: fillBinding=true (IDataBindingResolver), organizationId?, reportingPeriodId?
POST   /api/v1/forms                 # Create
PUT    /api/v1/forms/{id}            # Full update
DELETE /api/v1/forms/{id}            # Delete

GET    /api/v1/submissions                    # List
GET    /api/v1/submissions/{id}                # Get one
POST   /api/v1/submissions                     # Create (409 nếu trùng Form+Org+Period)
GET    /api/v1/submissions/{id}/presentation  # Get ReportPresentation (WorkbookJson, fileSize)
POST   /api/v1/submissions/{id}/upload-excel  # Multipart form-data, file .xlsx/.xls
```

## Controller Pattern
```csharp
[ApiController]
[Route("api/v1/[controller]")]
[Authorize]
public class FormsController : ControllerBase
{
    [HttpGet("{id}")]
    [ProducesResponseType<ApiResponse<FormDto>>(200)]
    [ProducesResponseType(404)]
    public async Task<IActionResult> Get(int id)
    {
        var result = await _formService.GetAsync(id);
        return result.ToActionResult();
    }
}
```

## Response Wrapper
```csharp
public class ApiResponse<T>
{
    public bool Success { get; set; }
    public T? Data { get; set; }
    public string? Message { get; set; }
    public List<string>? Errors { get; set; }
}
```

## Status Codes
- 200: Success with data
- 201: Created (with Location header)
- 204: Success no content (DELETE)
- 400: Validation error
- 401/403: Auth errors
- 404: Not found
- 500: Server error (log, don't expose details)

## List endpoint cho resource phân cấp (ParentId / TreePath / Level)

Khi entity có quan hệ cha–con (Organization, Menu, ReferenceEntity, …):

- **Query param `all`** (bool, optional): Khi `all=true` trả về **toàn bộ** bản ghi (flat), không filter theo parentId. Khi không truyền hoặc `all=false` giữ hành vi hiện tại (vd. parentId null = chỉ gốc).
- **Ví dụ:** `GET /api/v1/organizations?all=true&includeInactive=true` → toàn bộ đơn vị (flat) để FE build cây.

**Tài liệu:** [HIERARCHICAL_DATA_BASE_AND_RULE.md](docs/de_xuat_trien_khai/HIERARCHICAL_DATA_BASE_AND_RULE.md). **Rule FE:** bcdt-hierarchical-data.

## Don't
- Don't return 200 for errors
- Don't put business logic in controllers
- Don't expose stack traces
